parameters.kubeConfig:
apiVersion: v1
clusters:
- cluster:
    server: https://B182759F93D251942CB146063F57036B.yl4.eu-west-1.eks.amazonaws.com
    certificate-authority-data: 
  name: hellman
contexts:
- context:
    cluster: hellman
    user: hellman-saml
  name: hellman-saml
current-context: hellman-saml
kind: Config
preferences: {}
users:
- name: hellman-saml
  user:
    exec:
      apiVersion: client.authentication.k8s.io/v1alpha1
      command: aws-iam-authenticator
      args:
        - "token"
        - "-i"
        - "hellman"
      env:
        - name: AWS_PROFILE
          value: "saml"
